## WAF Rule Reference

| Rule | Pattern Blocked | Severity |
|------|----------------|----------|
| SQLi_UNION | `UNION SELECT` | HIGH |
| SQLi_COMMENT | `--`, `#`, `/**/` | MEDIUM |
| SQLi_BOOLEAN | `OR 1=1`, `AND 1=1` | MEDIUM |
| SQLi_SLEEP | `SLEEP()`, `WAITFOR` | HIGH |
| SQLi_DROP | `DROP TABLE`, `TRUNCATE` | CRITICAL |

